===[[Etymology]]===
Greek ''demos'' people (more at ?) + ''kratia'' fr. ''kratos'' government
=== Noun ===

'''democracy'''

#[[Government]] usually under the direct or representative rule of the [[people]] of the country.  Usually has an [[election]] for a leader or other government administrators.

